title: La meglio gioventù
actors: Luigi Lo Cascio, Alessio Boni, Adriana Asti, Sonia Bergamasco, Fabrizio Gifuni, Maya Sansa, Valentina Carnelutti, Jasmine Trinca, Andrea Tidona, Lidia Vitale, Claudio Gioè, Paolo Bonanni, Giovanni Scifoni, Riccardo Scamarcio, Camilla Filippi
description: An Italian epic that follows the lives of two brothers, from the 1960s to the 2000s.
